-- (a) provenance reports show authenticatedExecute=false, and (b) the
-- default exposes the new function to anon clients implicitly. Drop the
-- 3-arg overload to avoid split behavior and explicitly revoke from
-- public + grant to authenticated on the 4-arg signature.
--
-- P2: finalize_workspace_document_upload / finalize_org_document_upload
-- unconditionally insert a fresh row on every call. Retries (timeout,
-- double-submit) duplicate the user's document. Mirror the project
-- upload finalize pattern by checking whether a document_version
-- already references this intent's storage object and returning the
-- existing record instead of reinserting. Linkage is via storage_object
-- id rather than an upload_intents.<table>_id column so the curated
-- contract (which currently excludes workspace_documents and friends)
-- doesn't need to widen.

